•	Improved Efficiency: Streamlined hospital processes with reduced administrative burden, leading to better patient care.
•	Enhanced Patient Experience: Patients can easily book appointments, receive reminders, and access their medical records anytime.
•	Secure Data Management: Secure storage and retrieval of patient data, ensuring data integrity and compliance with privacy regulations.
•	Optimized Resource Use: Better management of hospital resources, including doctors, rooms, and medical supplies.
•	Data Monetization for Patients: Patients will have more control over their medical data and can earn incentives by sharing anonymized data with researchers.
•	Actionable Insights: Detailed analytics and reporting provide hospital management with insights into operational performance, patient trends, and areas for improvement.
